WEBVTT

00:00.692 --> 00:02.960
<i>Previously on "Heartland":</i>

00:03.028 --> 00:04.461
<i>Why are you so
determined</i> <i>with this horse?</i>

00:05.864 --> 00:07.464
Oof!

00:07.532 --> 00:08.732
This horse is acting
exactly like Spartan did

00:08.799 --> 00:09.866
after the accident.

00:11.435 --> 00:13.069
He was this close
to being put down as well.

00:13.137 --> 00:13.937
<i>If Spartan can come back</i>
<i>from that,</i>

00:14.005 --> 00:15.404
<i>so can Alcatraz.</i>

00:16.607 --> 00:19.475
I need the brutal honest truth.

00:19.543 --> 00:21.210
Do you think Austin
is just using me?

00:22.446 --> 00:24.847
Ty, your dad...

00:24.914 --> 00:26.915
He's gone.

00:26.983 --> 00:28.651
He passed away.

00:31.287 --> 00:32.621
<i>I remember thinking</i> <i>that rock</i>

00:32.689 --> 00:34.389
<i>was the coolest thing</i>
<i>in the world.</i>

00:34.457 --> 00:36.659
And I grew up and I found out
it was worthless.

00:36.726 --> 00:38.627
Just fools gold.

00:38.695 --> 00:41.696
I hope you can find
a peaceful place for him.

00:42.665 --> 00:43.765
Eagle Lake.

00:45.000 --> 00:51.074
